{"tid":1888794,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"瓏驤有員工父母確診感染　ifc分店全部員工家居隔離","createTime":"2020-02-20T11:52:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T12:51:40.000Z","uid":246823,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e3ecb2d9948e6cb363fb1668842b22ee1ba14139","tid":1888794,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T11:52:21.000Z","msg":"2020-02-20 HKT 19:49<br />\n<br />\n本港昨日新增3宗新型冠狀病毒確診個案，LongChamp發表聲明表示，在中環 ifc 分店工作的一名女銷售僱員，其父母於昨日確診，ifc分店所有員工由即日起，會作家居隔離 14 天。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指，該名女銷售僱員沒有出現病徵，新型冠狀病毒測試結果呈陰性，現已根據衞生署要求進行 14 天檢疫。<br />\n<br />\n為確保公眾及員工安全，ifc 分店今天暫停營業，並安排了專業人員進行徹底的清潔服務和消毒程序，所有員工由即日起，會作家居隔離 14 天。"},{"pid":"17b4c05c654102154fefe445d8d1efe85dd895bc","tid":1888794,"uid":4139,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T11:53:10.000Z","msg":"返工攬炒法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4452e34d477267475226fddf408b9702b8a8b41","tid":1888794,"uid":88743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T11:54:24.000Z","msg":"之前好似話ifc有一半鬼佬唔戴口罩<br />\n班鬼佬點睇?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4105196bff38d7666e0b8ef80a2e2c57a32d5d34","tid":1888794,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T12:00:34.000Z","msg":"Longchamp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61502ebb34520d4c8dba606c117437546e88394d","tid":1888794,"uid":50386,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T12:01:23.000Z","msg":"瓏驤&lt;-第一次見呢個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ea71f850e93a667cdfd7bf71341958316f89682","tid":1888794,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61502ebb34520d4c8dba606c117437546e88394d","tid":1888794,"uid":50386,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"rep